<p>Thank you for your guidance and for confirming the wide range of acceptable gift cards for this transaction. Your assurance is greatly appreciated as we move towards the successful completion of the delivery process.</p>
<p>In line with your most recent instructions, I have acquired a Steam wallet gift card—they seem popular and reliable, and I wanted to ensure no further errors. I will ensure I follow the proper procedure this time by scratching off the panel on the back to reveal the necessary code.</p>
<p>However, before I proceed to scratch the card and send the details, I do have one final, small favor to ask for my records. Could you kindly confirm, as a final reassurance, the address or the specific branch of the United Nations office from which you're operating? Just a little detail to add to my documentation alongside your UN Delivery Agent title, before I excitedly await the copy of the insurance certificate and the flight schedule.</p>
<p>Once you provide this additional information, I will immediately scratch off the gift card panel and send over a crystal clear photo of the card code alongside the receipt, ensuring that your detailed instructions are meticulously followed.</p>
<p>The feeling of being so close to resolving this and receiving the ATM card gives me great joy and I am fully ready to cooperate with you in these final steps of our agreed-upon transaction.</p>
<p>Looking forward to your prompt response to finalize our preparations.</p>
<p>With best regards,</p>
