<p>Ash looked up at Lance with cautious gratitude, relieved that at least, for now, he wouldn't be forced into a situation he disliked. As the night wore on, both the giant jaguar and the tiny pardinensis cheetah found solace in each other's company, their connection growing stronger and more understanding with each passing day.</p></div>

